data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained brick home, perfectly suited for a growing family. Boasting 1,428 square feet, this spacious property offers 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing ample space for everyone. The brand new roof ensures durability and protects your investment. Additionally, the solar panels, to be fully paid off at closing, offer both energy efficiency and cost savings. The kitchen is a focal point, complete with a convenient island that provides extra storage and workspace. The entire home is adorned with tasteful tile flooring. Situated in far east El Paso, this property is conveniently located within walking distance to parks, providing endless opportunities for outdoor activities and family fun. Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your forever home!
